'''Keith Carter''' is an artist who specializes in computer illustrations. His work has appeared in [[Wikipedia:The Washington Post|''The Washington Post'']], [[Wikipedia:USA Today|''USA Today'']] and [[Wikipedia:National Geographic Magazine|''National Geographic'']]. He has also contributed to several [[Wikipedia:Nike, Inc.|Nike]] campaigns. Keith produced artwork for a number of trading cards in [[The Topps Company, Inc.|Topps's]] ''Star Wars Galaxy Series 3'' depicting scenes and characters from [[LucasArts|LucasArts Entertainment Company]] games.<ref>''Star Wars Galaxy Series 3''</ref>

